{"id": "1488197590318317698", "channel_id": "1433513650299076780", "type": 19, "author_id": "706246430582636624", "author_name": "spruzzetto", "author_bot": false, "content": "You will max the wheel of the event without problem. The question is, if it's worth to pull 16 copies of the same wheel on the standard banner, and why if so (It will take a lot of pulls and time). The answer is yes for some of them, and the priority is the one of Goliath, called Blade of the Titan. Reason is, once it will be at +12, you will be able to slot on your dps 2 SSR wheel. It will be a great power upgrade. \nSo, first, pull standard banner of Awakeners until you feel comfortable with your characters base. Then, switch to Wheel standard banner and pull Blade of the Titan. And remember, never use silver for standard pulls. Save silver for limited banners.", "timestamp": "2026-03-30T15:25:54.906000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": ["330139501022412800"], "reactions": [], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": "1488191371704537128", "has_thread": false, "thread_id": null, "flags": 0}
